column5: Just a note ,to say I'll be "off line" for 3 weeks. Heading to points South to the Carolina beaches.  No fishing, just relaxing, and maybe  a cup of Java at the 'Plummas,as we will be passing pretty close.  See ya'll in 3wks.

And I thought you said you were leaving Monday.  Have a great time Jack, maybe we'll hit the water when you return and you can show me where the fish are in Pigeon Lake, 'cause Beans sure don't know  Maureen
Give Art and Joe a big howdy for me.
Hope to see ya soon Jack. Joe
Sheese...the nerve of some people's children...  You, Jackie (RLG) and Cocoa have a great trip my friend and will see you when you return...
